    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including an engine that struggles to stay running and a transmission that requires a full overhaul. The body shows heavy wear with noticeable rust and denting, and the interior will need a complete restoration. Please be aware that it is not in drivable condition and will need to be towed.",
